XYZ-FIXTURE 1.0
==============

Plain test data with an unrecognised extension. The extractor maps
.xyz to no language and returns []. The Phase 2 service still emits a
file-level inventory entry with path, size, and mtime — that is the
ADR-017 D3 "degraded path" — but the file-level entry does not come
from this fixture-driven test.

This file deliberately contains text that resembles common keywords
("function foo", "class Bar", "interface Baz") to make sure the
extractor does not heuristically pretend to find symbols in unknown
languages.

  function foo() = nope, not extracted.
  class Bar     = also not extracted.
  interface Baz = nope.
  enum Quux     = nope.

End of fixture.
